<section class="section aerys-faq" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="sec-label">Common Questions</span>
    <h2 id="faq-title" style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.375rem);font-weight:800;text-align:center;line-height:1.2">
      Everything you need to know
    </h2>

    <div class="aerys-faq__list" role="list">

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq1">
          Can I suffocate using AERYS™ sleep strips?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq1" role="region">No. AERYS™ features a precision breathability channel that allows natural lip movement—your airway is never fully sealed. The strips promote nasal breathing, not restriction. If your mouth needs to open, the strip releases naturally.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">
          Will AERYS™ irritate my skin or facial hair?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq2" role="region">No. Our pharma-grade silicone adhesive was specifically validated for dermal sensitivity and facial hair compatibility. No acrylic, no latex, no harsh chemicals. If you experience any reaction within 30 nights, we refund in full.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq3">
          How is AERYS™ different from other mouth tapes?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq3" role="region">Three distinctions: (1) Pharma-grade silicone adhesive—not industrial acrylic. (2) Clinical breathability matrix—engineered precision, not guesswork. (3) Dermatologist-tested zero-residue release system that works on beards too.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq4">
          Why only 30, 90, and 180 nights? No 60?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq4" role="region">Because 60 nights is the gap between starting and transforming. The 30-Night Starter proves the concept. The 90-Night Protocol locks in the habit. The 180-Night Regimen makes it a lifestyle. 60 nights is where most competitors put their "medium" bundle — we eliminated it because it doesn't serve your biology.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq5">
          Is AERYS™ HSA/FSA eligible?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq5" role="region">Yes. AERYS™ qualifies as a medical wellness expense under HSA/FSA guidelines. You can use your health savings or flexible spending account to purchase any of our protocols.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="aerys-faq__trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq6">
          What's the cost per night for each pack?
          <svg class="aerys-faq__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 10.5L2 4.5h12z"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="aerys-faq__answer" id="faq6" role="region">
          Starter (30 Nights): $1.00/night<br>
          Best Seller (90 Nights): $0.67/night<br>
          Maximum Savings (180 Nights): $0.55/night — Best Value
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{ "name": "FAQ", "settings": [] }
{% endschema %}
